  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2495",
  "title": "XSS protection on hits breaks searchForFacetValues",
  "body": "When using both `escapeHits` on the hits widget and `searchForFacetValues` on a refinementList, the highlighted results of the SFFV will use the pre and post highlight tags of the hits.\r\n\r\n![2017-10-17 15 08 14](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/393765/31666615-22690f4e-b34d-11e7-99ef-4d2dde8d2b9e.gif)\r\n\r\nProposed solution:\r\n - make sure that the connectRefinementList implementations receives properly cleaned results\r\n - deprecate escapeHits at the widget level and move it to an instantsearch option\r\n\r\n@iam4x what do you think?",
